creator: KronEngineCompany™
descriptionHtml:
The main hero of this game is a cat named Flufy that aims for going back home. To reach this goal Flufy must collect fish on each Level, if it doesn't it won't get to the next level. Moreover Flufy will be haunted by a dog - Bob, because Flufy disturbed Bob accidentally. You will be interested with what will happen at the end.
Also, except Bob, you'll face more obstacles to get home. To overcome all difficulties you need to collect hidden bonuses in this game.
There will the store in the game where you can purchase all you need to complete the game more comfortable and quickly.
Draw your attention to the fact that you DO NOT HAVE TO DONATE to complete this game!
descriptionShort: Pixel 2D adventure game, cat Fluphy and dog Bob.
